c&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d569d16 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"d569d16\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h5 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Optimal Performance<\/h5>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6a1bed0 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"6a1bed0\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b27ff81 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"b27ff81\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Additionally, medical teams offer essential healthcare to prevent disease outbreaks and treat injuries caused by conflict. This assistance is not only a basic necessity but also a symbol of hope, showing refugees that they are not forgotten. The impact of humanitarian aid goes beyond immediate survival. It helps restore dignity, providing refugees with the resources they need to regain a sense of normalcy and begin rebuilding their lives in the face of adversity. Every donation, every volunteer effort, and every action counts in the fight for a better future for those affected by war.<\/p>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-419e8b3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-toggle\" data-id=\"419e8b3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"toggle.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-toggle\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-toggle-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h5 id=\"elementor-tab-title-6881\" class=\"elementor-tab-title\" data-tab=\"1\" role=\"button\" aria-controls=\"eleme